private void runTestClassAndAssertStats(Class<?> testClass, int expectedTestCount) throws Exception {     runTestsAndAssertCounters(testClass, expectedTestCount, 0, expectedTestCount, 0, 0). }

private void assertBehaviorForCleanTestCase() throws Exception {     runTestClassAndAssertStats(CleanTestCase.class, 1).     assertContextCacheStatistics("after clean test class", 1, cacheHits.get(), cacheMisses.incrementAndGet()). }
@AfterClass public static void verifyFinalCacheState() {     assertContextCacheStatistics("AfterClass", 0, cacheHits.get(), cacheMisses.get()). }
protected void assertApplicationContextWasAutowired() {     assertNotNull("The application context should have been autowired.", this.applicationContext). }
